Melbourne Gardens, Northampton Glee Contest part of 2nd Annual Contest organised by Northampton Temperance Band. Entries restricted to local bands. Reported in Northampton Herald 24th July 1886 Prizes: £5 and 13 guinea cornet, £3 and conductor's baton, £2. 4 bands competed.
